{"id":"7ae8769a-ee7d-4d4d-a9c2-96a8e72a2d78","name":"TenSura RPG ","description":"<p>In this Rpg you are able to play as charecter of choices from the world of that time, i got reincarnated as a slime or be a character of your own creation instead. you also get to choose when in the story you want to start your adventure at and where in the world.</p><p></p><p>Many of the rules of the world at that time, I got reincarnated as a slime such as the skill System and the monster system.</p><p></p><p>I have put a lot of work into this bot, I'm sorry if you run into some problems. This bot is also very complicated.</p><p></p><p>Not all story arcs are available at this time if you want them, please leave a comment.</p><p>List of story arcs that you can choose to start at.</p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://tensura.fandom.com/wiki/Empowerment\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Empowerment Arc</strong></a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://tensura.fandom.com/wiki/A_Disturbance_in_the_Forest\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>A Disturbance in the Forest Arc</strong></a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://tensura.fandom.com/wiki/Attack_of_the_Demon_Lord\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Attack of the Demon Lord Arc</strong></a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://tensura.fandom.com/wiki/A_Demon_Lord%27s_Awakening\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>A Demon Lord's Awakening Arc</strong></a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://tensura.fandom.com/wiki/The_Octagram_Soars\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>The Octagram Soars Arc</strong></a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://tensura.fandom.com/wiki/Conflict_Between_Saints_and_Monsters\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Conflict Between Saints and Monsters Arc</strong></a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://tensura.fandom.com/wiki/Opening_of_the_Monster_City\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Opening of the Monster City Arc</strong></a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://tensura.fandom.com/wiki/The_Eve_of_War\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>The Eve of War Arc</strong></a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://tensura.fandom.com/wiki/The_Imperial_Invasion\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>The Imperial Invasion Arc</strong></a></p><p></p><p>Location to start at.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\">The Great <strong>Jura</strong> <strong>Forest/ nation of tempest.</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\"><strong>The</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(247, 237, 237)\"><strong> </strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://tensura.fandom.com/wiki/Armed%20Nation%20of%20Dwargon\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(247, 237, 237)\"><strong>Armed Nation of Dwargon</strong></span></a></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>The </strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://tensura.fandom.com/wiki/Beast%20Kingdom%20of%20Eurazania\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>Beast Kingdom of Eurazania</strong></span></a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://tensura.fandom.com/wiki/Harpy%20Queendom%20of%20Fulbrosia\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>The Harpy Queendom of Fulbrosia</strong></span></a></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\"><strong>City of the Forgotten Dragon/ Milim's domain</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">The </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://tensura.fandom.com/wiki/Holy%20Empire%20of%20Lubelius\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>Holy Empire of Lubelius</strong></span></a></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>The Eastern Empire.</strong></span></p><p>The Sorcerous Dynasty of Sarion</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\"><strong>Ice Continent in the north.</strong></span></p><p></p><p></p>","personality":"","scena